---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Shopify Shipping Calculator — Free Tools for Sellers"
  description="Free calculators for Shopify sellers: shipping rates, profit margins, break-even analysis. No signup required."
>
  <section class="text-center py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Free Shopify Calculator Tools</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Quick, accurate calculators to help Shopify sellers price products, calculate shipping costs,
      and maximize profit margins.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-8">
    <a href="/shopify-hidden-fees-audit/" class="block border-2 border-orange-400 dark:border-orange-600 bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-950 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition md:col-span-2">
      <div class="text-xs font-medium text-orange-700 dark:text-orange-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">New — 5-Step Audit</div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Hidden Fees Audit — Find Your True Monthly Cost</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Answer 5 questions, get a full breakdown of every fee you pay: transaction charges, app stack, currency conversion, chargebacks, and more. Download as PDF.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/ltv-cac-calculator/" class="block border-2 border-teal-400 dark:border-teal-600 bg-teal-50 dark:bg-teal-950 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition md:col-span-2">
      <div class="text-xs font-medium text-teal-700 dark:text-teal-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">New — Unit Economics</div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">LTV:CAC Calculator — Customer Lifetime Value vs Acquisition Cost</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Enter AOV, purchase frequency, gross margin, and ad spend to calculate LTV:CAC ratio, payback period, and net LTV. Includes sensitivity table and improvement playbook.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/shopify-plan-comparison/" class="block border-2 border-indigo-400 dark:border-indigo-600 bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-950 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition md:col-span-2">
      <div class="text-xs font-medium text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">New — Plan Calculator</div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Plan Comparison Calculator — Basic vs Shopify vs Advanced vs Plus</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Enter your monthly revenue and AOV to see total fees for every Shopify plan. Includes break-even upgrade points and a revenue sensitivity table.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/breakeven-roas-calculator/" class="block border-2 border-blue-400 dark:border-blue-600 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-950 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition md:col-span-2">
      <div class="text-xs font-medium text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">New — Ad Spend Tool</div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Breakeven ROAS Calculator — Find Your Minimum ROAS</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Enter COGS, Shopify plan, and fixed costs to calculate your exact breakeven ROAS. Includes sensitivity table and channel breakdown for Meta, Google, TikTok.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/shopify-profit-calculator/" class="block border-2 border-green-400 dark:border-green-600 bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-950 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition md:col-span-2">
      <div class="text-xs font-medium text-green-700 dark:text-green-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">New — Flagship Tool</div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Real Profit Calculator — Full Monthly P&amp;L</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Revenue minus COGS, payment fees, plan cost, apps, marketing, shipping, and returns. See where every dollar goes with a live pie chart breakdown.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/shipping/" class="block border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-800 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-950 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
      <div class="text-xs font-medium text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">New — 280+ Cities</div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Shipping Rates by City</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Compare USPS, UPS, FedEx, and DHL rates from any US city to any destination. All 50 states covered.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/china-shipping/" class="block border border-purple-200 dark:border-purple-800 bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-950 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
      <div class="text-xs font-medium text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">New — 50 Countries</div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">China Shipping Rates</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">ePacket, DHL, FedEx International rates from China to 50+ countries. 2026 rates.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/shipping-calculator/" class="block border dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Shipping Rate Calculator</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Estimate USPS, UPS, and FedEx shipping costs by weight and destination zip code.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/profit-margin/" class="block border dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Profit Margin Calculator</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Calculate net profit after Shopify fees, payment processing, COGS, and shipping.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/break-even/" class="block border dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Break-Even Calculator</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Find the minimum units you need to sell to cover your fixed and variable costs.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/free-shipping-threshold/" class="block border dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Free Shipping Threshold Calculator</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Optimal free shipping threshold that boosts AOV without eating your margin.</p>
    </a>
  </section>
</Base>
